				Cleansing the market?
<br />

<br />
The invisible hand knows how to wash itself. No?
<br />

<br />
How can a man or a commitee cleanse an entire economic market?  You can't.  The charges I see here against this company is that they made a profit and there for owe 107% of it in taxes where other compnies inthe same market are paying 21% of their profit.
<br />

<br />
If there was something awry in the market then the market would cleanse itself. The only thing people can do it unbalance it more by interfering to the point of business assassination.  Its like suggesting that a guy is trying to still the waters of a pool by tossing stones at it.  He argues that he can set up symapthetic undulations from the stones and stop the constant wave action. All he needs do is sit back and let gravity and surface tension do thir natural work.<br />
