				</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>poppa wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">
<br />

<br />
You tell me if they are fraudulent.  I am not seeing evidence in the news (I'd like references if you have em <img src="images/smiles/smile.gif" alt="smile" border="0" /> )that there is fraud there, only that the courts arbitratily decided to tax this one company into oblivion because its CEO is active in political reform.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
